602
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,440
When the chips are down,

603
00:26:09,440 --> 00:26:11,640
I can always count on my son.

604
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:13,040
Our Xuan Yan comes through.

605
00:26:13,960 --> 00:26:14,800
