608
00:26:19,280 --> 00:26:20,480
Not only am I going to win,

609
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:24,240
I'm taking back Pine Crane Studio's business.

610
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:25,040
Yes, yes, yes!

611
00:26:25,440 --> 00:26:26,240
That's the spirit!

612
00:26:27,840 --> 00:26:30,400
Old Xuan and I taught Xuan Yan for over ten years.

613
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:32,000
Why would we fear that rookie?

614
00:26:32,120 --> 00:26:33,720
