615
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:36,160
We've all got your back. Don't worry.

616
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:40,240
An incense of devotion soars to the heavens,

617
00:26:44,600 --> 00:26:48,000
A white deer bears scriptures across the stone bridge.

618
00:26:50,280 --> 00:26:53,520
The Xuan ancestors paved the way through the clouds,

619
00:26:54,360 --> 00:26:57,480
Forever honored on the sacred altar.

