659
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:18,440
Today,

660
00:29:19,320 --> 00:29:21,160
he's finally meeting the real masters

661
00:29:25,480 --> 00:29:26,800
The lab test results are in.

662
00:29:27,040 --> 00:29:27,760
Yes.

663
00:29:27,840 --> 00:29:29,880
The materials and water source may be the same,

664
00:29:30,080 --> 00:29:32,480
