665
00:29:32,480 --> 00:29:33,560
Both meet the standard.

666
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:36,920
But for whiteness, uniformity,

667
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:40,000
and impurity tests, these three,

668
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:41,760
Group B's sample performs better.

669
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:43,200
Group B?

670
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:45,760
Isn't that the Xuan family's handmade paper?

671
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:46,840
Yes.

672
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:48,640
Alright, get back to work.

673
00:29:49,520 --> 00:29:50,600
