680
00:30:02,800 --> 00:30:05,000
Am I just a sightseeing tourist?

681
00:30:05,600 --> 00:30:06,520
Does my vote not count?

682
00:30:06,800 --> 00:30:07,600
Oh really?

683
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:09,360
You old rascal.

684
00:30:09,800 --> 00:30:11,880
If you're not a tourist, then speak up!

685
00:30:12,040 --> 00:30:13,000
If you kept quiet any longer,

686
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:14,440
I'd have thought you were dead.

687
00:30:15,320 --> 00:30:16,920
Well, if I died, it'd be from you old fools

688
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:18,160
