689
00:30:18,920 --> 00:30:20,400
Paper is meant to be used.

690
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:22,640
You're deciding without even testing it?

691
00:30:23,160 --> 00:30:25,680
Just because it's called "Ancient-Method Paper"?

692
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:28,280
Tianjin's buns are called "Goubuli" (Dogs Ignore).

693
00:30:28,280 --> 00:30:29,600
Try feeding one to a dog

694
00:30:29,760 --> 00:30:30,760
