695
00:30:31,840 --> 00:30:33,200
You are all experts here.

696
00:30:33,760 --> 00:30:36,240
Words and actions must be rigorous.

697
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:37,560
You have to be responsible.

698
00:30:37,760 --> 00:30:40,080
Don't just spout nonsense.

699
00:30:40,520 --> 00:30:41,160
Hold on, Old Jiang.

700
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:42,520
You're the one spouting nonsense.

701
00:30:42,600 --> 00:30:43,920
Ancient-Method Paper and Goubuli buns,

702
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:44,960
