703
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:46,000
Fine.

704
00:30:47,600 --> 00:30:48,560
Then let me ask you.

705
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:53,400
The paintings we're restoring are Ming and Qing.

706
00:30:54,320 --> 00:30:55,920
This Ancient-Method Paper of yours,

707
00:30:56,320 --> 00:31:00,600
