765
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:48,400
Don't mimic my nitpicking.

766
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:50,760
Just tell us which paper is better.

767
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:52,200
Speaking responsibly,

768
00:33:52,440 --> 00:33:55,280
the Xuan family's traditional handmade paper is superior.

769
00:33:56,120 --> 00:33:59,080
Natural ink absorption, lively and fluid.

770
00:34:00,400 --> 00:34:01,200
I have to admit,

771
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:03,440
it does have a certain spirit to it.

772
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:06,080
Master Jiang,

773
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:07,720
